 {"id":"bd-3hqvs","title":"Fix N+1 query pattern in querySessionCostWisps","description":"## Problem

`querySessionCostWisps()` (internal/cmd/costs.go:1010-1026) makes a separate `bd show` call for each wisp. With many session cost wisps, this creates O(n) subprocess calls.

## Location

internal/cmd/costs.go:1010-1026

## Solution

Batch the `bd show` calls - collect all wisp IDs first, then call `bd show id1 id2 id3...` once.

